1. install git; clone https://github.com/mykol71/mscloudserver.git

2. Install deps via cloud menu

3. Install AWS CLI via cloud menu

4. disable selinux (if not already)

5. create /etc/profile.d/tfrsync

6. add tfsupport user and set passwd

7. alter /etc/

8. add to sudoers

9. alter file to change default home folder

10. copy month script to /usr/local/bin

11. schedule recon.sh via cron
